      "x": 100, "y": 340, "width": 560, "height": 140,
      "text": "🧑  user sees candidate texts\n💬  discusses own subjective criteria\n🤖  strong model drafts labels\n✅  user accepts / revises / rejects\n📚  accepted pairs → gallery.jsonl",
