      "type": "text", "id": "phase2_body",
      "x": 800, "y": 340, "width": 560, "height": 140,
      "text": "📚  gallery is few-shot context\n⚡  cheap weak model runs inference\n🔖  produces label + confidence\n🔁  low-confidence → back to gallery\n📊  outputs labeled dataset",
      "originalText": "📚  gallery is few-shot context\n⚡  cheap weak model runs inference\n🔖  produces label + confidence\n🔁  low-confidence → back to gallery\n📊  outputs labeled dataset",
